column5: Charming 1940a bungalow in one of Austin's most desirable historic neighborhoods. Walkable location close to South Congress, Downtown, Convention Center. Goog_gle Fiber WiFi & 2 TVs. Fabulous Front Porch for enjoying the big oak trees, bird feeder & butterfly garden. Complimentary coffee, tea, snacks & natural spa products. Well equipped kitchen with pantry basics. Green cleaning products, pest control. Quiet, green neighborhood that is close to everything guests want to visit.
